    "incident_name": "Ecommerce Shopify order-webhook backfill unexpectedly long",
    "category": "Unexpected Long Running Job",
    "severity": "Sev-1 (Critical)",
    "description": "Unexpected Long Running Job incident on the Warehouse pipeline (RTL_WHS_ULRJ): ecommerce Shopify order-webhook backfill unexpectedly long.",
    "symptoms": "Hourly Shopify order sync went from 8min to 55min after a flash-sale event.",
    "root_cause": "A flash sale drove a 22x order spike within the hour, and the extractor's fixed page size (50) combined with sequential (non-mapped) pagination could not scale.",
    "business_impact": "Order data lag caused fulfillment prioritization logic to work off stale order data during the highest-value sales hour of the quarter.",
    "resolution": "Convert pagination loop to Airflow dynamic task mapping so pages fetch in parallel; raise page size to Shopify's max (250)."
  },
